quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  30,25,"Hino jeyaa e Ma'andeeji makko …óin: nde kammu ngun e leydi ndin daroto e yamiroore makko. Refti si O noddii on noddaandu ka leydi, e jaka onon ho…óon yalta (e genaale mon)."
  30,26,"Hino …óum woodani (Laamu, e takgoll e toppitagol) …ďeen won…ďe ka kammuuji e ka lesdi: kala ma…ď…ďe ko …óoftii…ďe mo."
  30,27,"Ko KaŇčko woni pu…ó…óu…óo tagoore, refti O ruttita nde; ko …óuum …ďuri newanaande mo. Homo woodani sifa …ďur…óo toowude ka kammuuji e ka leydi. Ko KaŇčko woni on pool…óo, √Ďee√Ī…óo on."
  30,28,"O piyanii on yeru immorde e ko'e-mon: hara no woodani on e …ďen …ďe njeyru…óon √Īaame mon, immorde e kafidal e kon ko min arsiki on, hara ho…óon pota e …óuum, ho…óon kulira …ďe wano kulirton ko'e-mon? Ko woni nii Min pensitirta Aayeeje …óen, wonan'de yim…ďe haqqiloo…ďe."
  30,29,"Si ko woni, too√Ī…ďe …ďen njokkirii belee…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ko aldaa e ganndal. Ko hommbo feewnata mo Alla majjini? Alanaa …ďe walloo…ďe."
  30,30,"Feewtinir yeeso maa ngon e diina kan √Īii…ďugol [e mun]. [∆äuum] ko tagoore Alla ngu O tagiri yim…ďe …ďen e mum - wa…ótitugol alaa e tagoore Alla nde -. Ko …óuum woni diina focciika kan; kono …ďur…ďe …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen nganndaa."
  30,31,"Hara ko on ruttotoo…ďe e makko; kulon Mo, √Īinnon juulde nden, wota on njeye e sirkoo…ďe …ďen."
  30,32,"(wano) …ďeya senndunoo…ďe diina mum kan, …ďe woni pecce-pecce, kala fedde no weltora ko woni ka mum kon."